ETCD is a distibuted reliable key-value store that is simple , secure and fast.
ETCD Cluster: Which stores informtion about 
 Nodes
 Pods
 Configs
 Secrets
 Accounts
 Roles
 Binding
 Other
When you run Kubecontrol get command from ETCD server.
If any change in cluster such as additional nodes, deploying pods & ReplicaSets are updating in ETCD server.
Once Updated in ETCD server , then considered the change is completed.
We can setup cluster two methods
 1. from strach - Download binaries 
 2. Kubeadm tool
 
